001package gbw.melange.common.elementary;
002
003/**
004 * <p>ElementState class.</p>
005 *
006 * @author GustavBW
007 * @version $Id: $Id
008 */
009public enum ElementState {
010    /**
011     * The content of this element is not quite ready, or the element itself isn't. Render a placeholder instead.
012     */
013    LOADING,
014    /**
015     * This element is currently not stable, it might be during a Cascading event or affected by one. <br/>
016     * Regardless, it might not be safe to cause changes to this element right now.
017     */
018    VOLATILE,
019    /**
020     * This element can receive updates and changes without issue.
021     */
022    STABLE,
023    /**
024     * Something went wrong, usually a failed OnInit. Regardless, this element is not expected to ever work quite right, so, do what you must.
025     */
026    ERROR;
027}
